The proportion of the number of equivocal annotations divided by all annotations for iNaturalist observations in the taxonomic family. A metric of how successful the annotation process for observations in that family.
A metric of accuracy for the annotations of only unequivocal records based on expert, gold standard observations.
A metric of accuracy for the annotations of all records (equivocal and unequivocal) based on expert, gold standard observations.
